Throttle or block certain applications (e.g., BitTorrent) Enterprises: Block social media on office networks Parental Controls: Block inappropriate websites Security: Detect malware or intrusion attempts What Our DPI Engine Does: User Traffic (PCAP) вҶ’ [DPI Engine] вҶ’ Filtered Traffic (PCAP)
                           вҶ“
                    - Identifies apps (YouTube, Facebook, etc.)
